    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><h2 id="title-��ѧPython���������ݽu-1"><a href="#title-��ѧPython���������ݽu-1" class="headerlink" title="title:��ѧPython���������ݽṹ(1)"></a>title:��ѧPython���������ݽṹ(1)</h2><p>��ӭ�����ҵ�blog��<br>���ڹ�����Ҫ�͸��˰��ã�����Ҫѧϰһ�Žű����ԣ�������ѡ������ѧPython����ϵ����Ϊ�ҵ�ѧϰ��¼��   </p><h2 id="Hello-world"><a href="#Hello-world" class="headerlink" title="Hello world"></a>Hello world</h2><p>Ҫ�������ϳ��ֵĵ�һ�仰��ʲô���ǵ�Ȼ�� “Hello world!”��   </p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#!/usr/bin/python</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#coding:utf-8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> <span class="string">&quot;hello world!&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>����shell�ű�һ����python��Ҫ�ڵ�һ��ָ����������#!/usr/bin/python<br>#coding:utf-8 ������˴���ı��뷽ʽ<br>print��ҿ϶��͸���İ���ˣ��Ͼ�C�Ǵ�ѧ���޿Σ��ֶ�������<br>���Ҳһ�������ˣ���C�Ĳ�֮ͬ�����У�ÿ�����Ľ�βû�зֺš�   </p><h2 id="���͡�������-int��float"><a href="#���͡�������-int��float" class="headerlink" title="���͡�������(int��float)"></a>���͡�������(int��float)</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="number">2.0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> a+b</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>����Ҹо�ûɶ��˵�ģ����C���ԣ��ڸ�ֵʱ����ָ�������ˣ����������ˣ���ʹ�ǹ������ַ���Ҳ���Զ�ʶ��Ϊlong long ���ͣ�ֵ��˵��һ������������ʱֻҪ������һ���Ǹ����ͣ�����Ҳ�Ǹ�����   </p><h2 id="�ַ������б�-string��list"><a href="#�ַ������б�-string��list" class="headerlink" title="�ַ������б�(string��list)"></a>�ַ������б�(string��list)</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = <span class="string">&quot;www.googel.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> a</span><br><span class="line">alist = [<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="string">&quot;3&quot;</span>,<span class="string">&quot;hello&quot;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> alist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>�ַ�����Cһ����������������������ͬ��C���������ѡ������Ҳ����ѡ��˫����<br>�б��е�Ԫ�ؿ����Ǹ��ֲ�ͬ���������ͣ�����������Ŀ�����ɾ�Ĳ��   </p><h3 id="�ַ�����һ�Է���"><a href="#�ַ�����һ�Է���" class="headerlink" title="�ַ�����һ�Է���"></a>�ַ�����һ�Է���</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">b = <span class="string">&quot;Www.googel.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">c = b.split(<span class="string">&quot;.&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> c</span><br><span class="line">d = <span class="string">&quot;.&quot;</span>.join(c)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>split����ĳ���ַ����ַ������<br>join����ĳ���ַ����б����ӳ��ַ���<br>����������������о��ܿ���Ч������סֱ�ӵ��þͺ�   </p><h3 id="�б���һЩ����"><a href="#�б���һЩ����" class="headerlink" title="�б���һЩ����"></a>�б���һЩ����</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">alist.extend(&quot;hello&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">#alist.apend(&quot;hello&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">print alist</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print alist.count(3)</span><br><span class="line">print alist.index(1)</span><br><span class="line">alist.insert(0,3)</span><br><span class="line">print alist</span><br><span class="line">alist.reverse()</span><br><span class="line">print alist</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">alist.sort()</span><br><span class="line">print alist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>extend��apend�������б������ӣ���ͬ����extend�ǰ�Ԫ�����ӣ�apend���������ӣ�ʲô��˼�أ��������һ�¾��ܿ����������Ϊѧϰ�����Ǳ�����Ե�ѧϰ��ֻ���Լ������ó����ĲŻ�������<br>count��index���ǲ����б��е�Ԫ�أ�count�ǰ����ݲ��ң�index�ǰ��������ҡ�count�ǲ����б�����û�����Ԫ�أ�index���ǲ����б��еĵ�n��Ԫ��<br>insert�����������������������������б��е�ĳ��λ������ĳ��Ԫ�أ���������Ҫ������������һ������ָ��λ�ã��ڶ�������ָ��Ҫ���ӵ�Ԫ��<br>reverse�ǽ��б��е�Ԫ�ط����������У�sort�������������б�   </p><h2 id="Ԫ��-tupel"><a href="#Ԫ��-tupel" class="headerlink" title="Ԫ��(tupel)"></a>Ԫ��(tupel)</h2><p>‘’’python<br>tu = 1,2,3,”hello”<br>print tu<br>‘’’<br>�����˵һ��Ԫ����б�������<br>Tuple �� list �����ٶȿ졣�����������һ��ֵ�ĳ�����������ΨһҪ���������ǲ��ϵر���������ʹ�� tuple ���� list<br>����Բ���Ҫ�޸ĵ����ݽ��� ��д������������ʹ�������ȫ��ʹ�� tuple ������ list ��ͬӵ��һ�������� assert ��䣬˵����һ�����ǳ������������Ҫ�ı���Щֵ������Ҫִ�� tuple �� list ��ת�� (��Ҫʹ��һ������ĺ���)<br>Tuples ������ dictionary���ֵ䣬����Ҫ������ �б����� key������ list ���С�Dictionary key �����ǲ��ɱ�ġ�Tuple �����ǲ��ɸı�ģ������������һ�� list �� tuple���Ǿ���Ϊ�ǿɱ���ˣ����� dictionary key ���ǲ���ȫ�ġ�ֻ���ַ����������������� dictionary ��ȫ��tuple �ſ������� dictionary key<br>Tuples ���������ַ�����ʽ����   </p><h2 id="����"><a href="#����" class="headerlink" title="����"></a>����</h2><p>��һ��дblog��Ҳ�ǵ�һ����Markdown���кܶ಻�㣬����������Ż��͸�������<br>ֻ��������һ�����Ż���������������</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
